  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nThere are instances the app hangs a bit if there are network issues. we should improve it so it can tolerate these better. for instance:\r\n\r\n1. open stickers menu and look for a free sticker\r\n2. turn off your network on your machine\r\n3. click to get stickers\r\n\r\nresult: app hangs until the network connections comes back",
